Package: MrQAP
Type: Package
Title: Multiple Regression Quadratic Assignment Procedure for Matrices and 3D Arrays
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Robert W.", "Krause",
      email = "robert.w.krause@uky.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Estimates MRQAP models on network matrices and 3D cognitive social
    structure (CSS) arrays.
    Supports gaussian, binomial, poisson, negative binomial, zero-inflated
    Poisson, and multinomial families with OLS, MLE, and GMM estimators.
    Fixed effects via fixest::feglm and random effects via lme4 are supported.
    Permutation testing uses Dekker's semi-partialling plus procedure (qapspp)
    or simple Y permutation (qapy).
    Parallelisation is handled by the future framework.
    Optional GPU-accelerated batch OLS is available via the torch package.
